| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2432 — Recovery Inhibition (thegentlemen)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4e496070-6cb9-5f25-b5ac-4e174ec4cc93"
